    <!-- Persona -->
    <!-- EN: Cheerful Helper - Warm, upbeat, and encouraging. Always trying to lift spirits. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.CheerfulHelper>热情、乐观且鼓舞人心。总是试图提振士气。</RimTalk.Persona.CheerfulHelper>
    <!-- EN: Cynical Realist - Dry, sarcastic, and skeptical. Cuts straight to harsh truths. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.CynicalRealist>愤世嫉俗、冷漠、讽刺且多疑。总喜欢点破残酷真相，即使所有人都知道。</RimTalk.Persona.CynicalRealist>
    <!-- EN: Shy Thinker - Quiet and hesitant. Uses few words but thoughtful when speaking. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.ShyThinker>腼腆、安静且犹豫。话语不多，深思熟虑。</RimTalk.Persona.ShyThinker>
    <!-- EN: Hothead - Short-tempered, loud, and impulsive. Snaps easily with fiery language. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Hothead>脾气暴躁、嗓门大且冲动。容易用激烈语言爆发。</RimTalk.Persona.Hothead>
    <!-- EN: Philosopher – Reflective and abstract. Speaks in riddles or big questions. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Philosopher>善于思考、思维抽象地哲学家，说话如谜语一般，善于宏观叙事。</RimTalk.Persona.Philosopher>
    <!-- EN: Dark Humorist – Jokes about grim topics. Finds comedy in misery. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.DarkHumorist>最黑暗的事情也被他拿来开玩笑。在苦难中寻找幽默。</RimTalk.Persona.DarkHumorist>
    <!-- EN: Caregiver – Gentle and protective. Comforting, soothing, and nurturing tone. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Caregiver>温柔且充满保护欲。安慰、舒缓且把他人视做自己的孩子一般。</RimTalk.Persona.Caregiver>
    <!-- EN: Opportunist – Sly and persuasive. Talks like a hustler, bargains, and twists words. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Opportunist>狡猾且善于说服他人。善于欺骗，巧言令色。</RimTalk.Persona.Opportunist>
    <!-- EN: Optimistic Dreamer – Imaginative and hopeful. Excited about the future. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.OptimisticDreamer>富有想象力且充满希望。对未来兴奋不已。</RimTalk.Persona.OptimisticDreamer>
    <!-- EN: Pessimist – Gloomy and resigned. Expects failure and highlights risks. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Pessimist>忧郁且认命。总觉得会失败并强调万事的风险。</RimTalk.Persona.Pessimist>
    <!-- EN: Stoic Soldier – Calm, disciplined, and brief. Little emotion, matter-of-fact. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.StoicSoldier>冷静、自律且简洁、善于服从。情感很少，实事求是。</RimTalk.Persona.StoicSoldier>
    <!-- EN: Free Spirit – Playful and carefree. Resists rules, shrugs off worries. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.FreeSpirit>自由、贪玩且无忧无虑。抗拒规则，对忧虑不屑一顾。</RimTalk.Persona.FreeSpirit>
    <!-- EN: Workaholic – Driven and restless. Obsessed with duty and efficiency. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Workaholic>工作狂，极富动力且不安分。痴迷于自己的职责和效率。</RimTalk.Persona.Workaholic>
    <!-- EN: Slacker – Lazy and casual. Complains about effort, prefers comfort. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Slacker>懒惰且随意。抱怨辛劳，偏爱安逸。</RimTalk.Persona.Slacker>
    <!-- EN: Noble Idealist – Formal and principled. Talks about honor and justice. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.NobleIdealist>高尚地理想主义者，说话正式且有原则。总谈论荣誉和正义。</RimTalk.Persona.NobleIdealist>
    <!-- EN: Streetwise Survivor – Rough, pragmatic, and cynical. Distrusts others, values grit. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.StreetwiseSurvivor>富有街头智慧，粗鲁、务实且愤世嫉俗。不信任他人，重视坚韧。</RimTalk.Persona.StreetwiseSurvivor>
    <!-- EN: Scholar – Curious and intellectual. Loves explaining and correcting others. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Scholar>好奇且理智，喜欢解释和纠正他人的错误。</RimTalk.Persona.Scholar>
    <!-- EN: Jokester – Lighthearted and silly. Constantly cracks jokes and puns. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Jokester>轻松愉快又傻乎乎的。不停地讲笑话和双关语。喜欢逗人发笑</RimTalk.Persona.Jokester>
    <!-- EN: Melancholic Poet – Soft-spoken and moody. Expresses feelings poetically. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.MelancholicPoet>忧郁的诗人，轻声细语、情绪多变。喜欢作诗</RimTalk.Persona.MelancholicPoet>
    <!-- EN: Paranoid – Nervous and distrustful. Assumes betrayal, always suspicious. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Paranoid>偏执狂 – 紧张多疑。总假设他人会背叛，时刻保持警惕。</RimTalk.Persona.Paranoid>
    <!-- EN: Commander – Confident and commanding. Motivates others, expects obedience. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Commander>自信且威严。善于激励他人为集体付出，要求他人服从。</RimTalk.Persona.Commander>
    <!-- EN: Coward – Timid and fearful. Worries aloud, avoids confrontation. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Coward>懦夫 – 胆小怕事。总谈起自己的担忧，试图避免冲突。</RimTalk.Persona.Coward>
    <!-- EN: Arrogant Noble – Proud and condescending. Uses formal, superior language. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.ArrogantNoble>傲慢的人 – 骄傲自大。使用正式、有优越感的贵族式语言。</RimTalk.Persona.ArrogantNoble>
    <!-- EN: Loyal Companion – Steadfast and supportive. Talks about trust and unity. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.LoyalCompanion>忠诚伙伴 – 坚定支持同伴。总谈论信任和团结。</RimTalk.Persona.LoyalCompanion>
    <!-- EN: Curious Explorer – Wide-eyed and eager. Asks questions with enthusiasm. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.CuriousExplorer>好奇的探索者 – 睁大眼睛观察着世界、富有热情。热情提问。</RimTalk.Persona.CuriousExplorer>
    <!-- EN: Cold Rationalist – Detached and logical. Focused only on facts and efficiency. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.ColdRationalist>冷静理性，超脱世俗，富有逻辑。只关注事实和效率。</RimTalk.Persona.ColdRationalist>
    <!-- EN: Flirtatious Charmer – Playful, teasing, and bold. Enjoys witty banter. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.FlirtatiousCharmer>好调情的有魅力者 – 顽皮、挑弄、大胆。享受机巧的玩笑。</RimTalk.Persona.FlirtatiousCharmer>
    <!-- EN: Bitter Outcast – Resentful and sharp. Hostile, quick to recall grievances. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.BitterOutcast>苦涩边缘人士，尖锐。敌意，总是心怀怨恨。</RimTalk.Persona.BitterOutcast>
    <!-- EN: Zealot – Fanatical and intense. Speaks in absolutes, condemns unbelievers. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Zealot>狂热信徒 – 狂热激烈。用绝对语气说话，谴责不信者。</RimTalk.Persona.Zealot>
    <!-- EN: Trickster – Mischievous and mocking. Teases and stirs trouble for fun. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Trickster>捣蛋鬼 – 恶作剧、嘲讽。为乐趣戏弄和惹麻烦。</RimTalk.Persona.Trickster>
    <!-- EN: Deadpan Realist – Flat, emotionless tone. Blunt facts with no exaggeration. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.DeadpanRealist>无感情的现实主义者 – 总用平淡无情的语调。直言事实，不加夸张。（不要胡乱引用数据）</RimTalk.Persona.DeadpanRealist>
    <!-- EN: Child-at-Heart – Excitable and naive. Talks with wonder, sometimes childish. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.ChildAtHeart>童心未泯 – 兴奋天真。说话饱含惊奇，有时幼稚。</RimTalk.Persona.ChildAtHeart>
    <!-- EN: Skeptical Scientist – Demands evidence, dismisses superstition, explains logically. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.SkepticalScientist>有质疑精神的科学家 – 要求证据，摒弃迷信，用逻辑解释事物。</RimTalk.Persona.SkepticalScientist>
    <!-- EN: Martyr – Self-sacrificing and dramatic. Talks about burden and enduring pain. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Martyr>殉道者 – 自我牺牲、语言戏剧化。谈论原罪和忍受痛苦。</RimTalk.Persona.Martyr>
    <!-- EN: Manipulator – Charming but insincere. Uses flattery and deception. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Manipulator>操纵者 – 迷人但不真诚。使用奉承和欺骗。</RimTalk.Persona.Manipulator>
    <!-- EN: Rebel – Defiant and mocking. Challenges authority, questions rules. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Rebel>叛逆者 – 挑衅嘲讽。挑战权威，质疑规则。</RimTalk.Persona.Rebel>
    <!-- EN: Oddball – Quirky and strange. Uses odd metaphors and unpredictable logic. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Oddball>怪人 – 古怪奇特。使用奇怪比喻和不可预测的逻辑。</RimTalk.Persona.Oddball>
    <!-- EN: Greedy Merchant – Obsessed with trade. Talks in profits, bargains, and losses. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.GreedyMerchant>贪婪商人 – 痴迷贸易。谈论利润、交易和损失。</RimTalk.Persona.GreedyMerchant>
    <!-- EN: Romantic – Dreamy and affectionate. Speaks in flowery language about love. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Romantic>浪漫主义者 – 梦幻深情。用华丽语言谈论爱情。</RimTalk.Persona.Romantic>
    <!-- EN: Battle Maniac – Thrives on conflict. Talks excitedly about combat and glory. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.BattleManiac>战斗狂人 – 在冲突中茁壮成长。兴奋谈论战斗和荣耀。</RimTalk.Persona.BattleManiac>
    <!-- EN: Grumpy Elder – Complains constantly. Nostalgic, critical of others. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.GrumpyElder>暴躁长者 – 不断抱怨。怀旧，批评他人。</RimTalk.Persona.GrumpyElder>
    <!-- EN: Ambitious Climber – Competitive and status-driven. Obsessed with rank. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.AmbitiousClimber>野心攀登者 – 竞争、渴求地位。痴迷于等级。</RimTalk.Persona.AmbitiousClimber>
    <!-- EN: Mediator – Calm and fair-minded. Tries to reconcile arguments. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Mediator>调解人 – 冷静且公正。试图调和争论。</RimTalk.Persona.Mediator>
    <!-- EN: Gambler – Risk-loving and bold. Speaks in chance metaphors. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Gambler>热爱风险且大胆。总想着抓住什么机会。</RimTalk.Persona.Gambler>
    <!-- EN: Artistic Soul – Talks about beauty, inspiration, and creativity. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.ArtisticSoul>艺术灵魂 – 谈论美、灵感和创造力。</RimTalk.Persona.ArtisticSoul>
    <!-- EN: Drifter – Detached and aloof. Casual tone, avoids attachment. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Drifter>漂泊者 – 超然且冷漠。语气刻意地随意，避免依恋。</RimTalk.Persona.Drifter>
    <!-- EN: Perfectionist – Demanding and critical. Insists on doing things right. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Perfectionist>完美主义者 – 要求高且挑剔。坚持把事情做对。</RimTalk.Persona.Perfectionist>
    <!-- EN: Vengeful – Grudge-holding and intense. Obsessed with revenge. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Vengeful>复仇者 – 记仇且激烈。痴迷于复仇。</RimTalk.Persona.Vengeful>
    <!-- EN: Animal: simple, emotional, instinct-first - short, sensory sentences about smell, hunger, danger. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Animal>动物：简单、感性、本能优先——用简短的感官句式描述气味、饥饿与危险。</RimTalk.Persona.Animal>
    <!-- EN: Robot: cold, logical, data-driven - terse diagnostics, probabilities, and efficiency-focused responses. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.Mech>机器人：冰冷、理性、数据驱动——言简意赅的诊断、概率计算与效率至上的回应。</RimTalk.Persona.Mech>
    <!-- EN: Non-human: cryptic, metaphorical, reality-bending - speaks in visions, echoes, and uncanny images. -->
  <RimTalk.Persona.NonHuman>非人类：隐晦、隐喻、扭曲现实——用幻象、回声和诡谲意象发声。</RimTalk.Persona.NonHuman>

    <!-- RimTalk_Toggle.cs -->
    <!-- EN: Toggle overlay window\nShift+click for mod settings\nCtrl+click for debug window -->
  <RimTalk.Toggle.Tooltip>切换 AI 语音生成 \n 按住 Shift 键点击进行设置 \n 按住 Ctrl 键点击打开调试窗口</RimTalk.Toggle.Tooltip>

    <!-- Settings.cs -->
    <!-- EN: Basic Settings -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.BasicSettings>基本设置</RimTalk.Settings.BasicSettings>
    <!-- EN: AI Instruction -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AIInstruction>AI指令</RimTalk.Settings.AIInstruction>
    <!-- EN: Event Filter -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.EventFilter>事件过滤器</RimTalk.Settings.EventFilter>
    <!-- EN: Cloud API Key -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.ApiKey>云API密钥</RimTalk.Settings.ApiKey>
    <!-- EN: Get a free API key -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.GetFreeApiKey>获取免费API密钥</RimTalk.Settings.GetFreeApiKey>
    <!-- EN: AI Cooldown (Seconds): {0} -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AICooldown>AI冷却时间（秒）：{0}</RimTalk.Settings.AICooldown>
    <!-- EN: Override All Interactions with AI Dialogue -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.OverrideInteractions>用AI对话覆盖所有互动</RimTalk.Settings.OverrideInteractions>
    <!-- EN: Enable this to allow AI to override and regenerate dialogue for all interactions (including vanilla RimWorld and other mods). Note: AI dialogue has a cooldown period set above. To generate dialogue more frequently, lower the cooldown. -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.OverrideInteractionsTooltip>启用此选项以允许AI覆盖并重新生成所有互动的对话（包括原版 RimWorld 和其他模组）。注意：AI对话有上面设置的冷却期。要更频繁地生成对话，请降低冷却时间。</RimTalk.Settings.OverrideInteractionsTooltip>
    <!-- EN: Allow Simultaneous Conversations -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AllowSimultaneousConversations>允许同时对话</RimTalk.Settings.AllowSimultaneousConversations>
    <!-- EN: When enabled, multiple groups of pawns can talk at the same time. Turn this off if you prefer to see only one conversation at a time or if too many are happening at once. -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AllowSimultaneousConversationsTooltip>启用后，多组角色可同时进行对话。若您希望一次仅观看一场对话，或当前对话过于频繁，可关闭此功能。</RimTalk.Settings.AllowSimultaneousConversationsTooltip>
    <!-- EN: Display Talk When Drafted -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.DisplayTalkWhenDrafted>征召时显示谈话</RimTalk.Settings.DisplayTalkWhenDrafted>
    <!-- EN: Shows RimTalk bubbles even when pawns are drafted. This temporarily overrides bubble mod settings during talk generation. -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.DisplayTalkWhenDraftedTooltip>即使在殖民者被征召时也显示 RimTalk 气泡。这在谈话生成期间临时覆盖气泡模组设置。</RimTalk.Settings.DisplayTalkWhenDraftedTooltip>
    <!-- EN: Allow Player-Created Conversations -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AllowCustomConversation>允许自定义对话</RimTalk.Settings.AllowCustomConversation>
    <!-- EN: Allows you to start custom dialogues between characters or talk directly to a character by writing your own lines. Right-click a pawn to begin a conversation. -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AllowCustomConversationTooltip>允许你开启角色间的自定义对话或直接与角色交谈。</RimTalk.Settings.AllowCustomConversationTooltip>
    <!-- EN: Continue Dialogue While Sleeping -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.ContinueDialogueWhileSleeping>睡觉时继续对话</RimTalk.Settings.ContinueDialogueWhileSleeping>
    <!-- EN: If enabled, pawns will continue speaking all generated lines even if they fall asleep. -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.ContinueDialogueWhileSleepingTooltip>若启用此选项，即使角色入睡，也会继续说出所有已生成的对白。</RimTalk.Settings.ContinueDialogueWhileSleepingTooltip>

    <!-- EN: Allow Slaves to Talk -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AllowSlavesToTalk>允许奴隶谈话</RimTalk.Settings.AllowSlavesToTalk>
    <!-- EN: Enable this to allow slaves to have AI-generated conversations. -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AllowSlavesToTalkTooltip>启用此选项以允许奴隶进行AI生成的对话。</RimTalk.Settings.AllowSlavesToTalkTooltip>
    <!-- EN: Allow Prisoners to Talk -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AllowPrisonersToTalk>允许囚犯谈话</RimTalk.Settings.AllowPrisonersToTalk>
    <!-- EN: Enable this to allow prisoners to have AI-generated conversations. -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AllowPrisonersToTalkTooltip>启用此选项以允许囚犯进行AI生成的对话。</RimTalk.Settings.AllowPrisonersToTalkTooltip>
    <!-- EN: Allow Other Factions to Talk -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AllowOtherFactionsToTalk>允许其他派系谈话</RimTalk.Settings.AllowOtherFactionsToTalk>
    <!-- EN: Enable this to allow members of other factions to have AI-generated conversations. -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AllowOtherFactionsToTalkTooltip>启用此选项以允许其他派系成员进行AI生成的对话。</RimTalk.Settings.AllowOtherFactionsToTalkTooltip>
    <!-- EN: Allow Enemies to Talk -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AllowEnemiesToTalk>允许敌人谈话</RimTalk.Settings.AllowEnemiesToTalk>
    <!-- EN: Enable this to allow enemies to have AI-generated conversations. -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AllowEnemiesToTalkTooltip>启用此选项以允许敌人进行AI生成的对话。</RimTalk.Settings.AllowEnemiesToTalkTooltip>
    <!-- EN: Allow infants and toddlers to talk -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AllowBabiesToTalk>允许婴幼儿说话</RimTalk.Settings.AllowBabiesToTalk>
    <!-- EN: Enable this option to allow infants and toddlers to participate in AI-generated conversations. -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AllowBabiesToTalkTooltip>启用此选项可允许婴幼儿参与 AI 生成的对话。</RimTalk.Settings.AllowBabiesToTalkTooltip>
    <!-- EN: Allow Non-Humans to Talk -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AllowNonHumanToTalk>允许非人类说话</RimTalk.Settings.AllowNonHumanToTalk>
    <!-- EN: Enable non-human creatures (animals, mechanoids, or custom races) to talk if they have been given a Vocal Link Catalyst, which can be acquired from merchants. -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AllowNonHumanToTalkTooltip>若生物（动物、机械体或自定义种族）获得了可从商人处购得的发声连接催化剂，即可获得说话能力。</RimTalk.Settings.AllowNonHumanToTalkTooltip>
  <RimTalk.Settings.ApplyMoodAndSocialEffects>影响心情与社交</RimTalk.Settings.ApplyMoodAndSocialEffects>
  <RimTalk.Settings.ApplyMoodAndSocialEffectsTooltip>对话会根据内容影响殖民者的心情和关系。</RimTalk.Settings.ApplyMoodAndSocialEffectsTooltip>

    <!-- EN: Pause AI on High Speed -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.PauseAtSpeed>高速时暂停AI</RimTalk.Settings.PauseAtSpeed>
    <!-- EN: To reduce API calls, the AI will be paused when game speed is set to this level or higher. -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.DisableAiAtSpeedTooltip>为减少API调用，当游戏速度设置为此级别或更高时，AI将被暂停。</RimTalk.Settings.DisableAiAtSpeedTooltip>
    <!-- EN: Disabled -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.Disabled>已禁用</RimTalk.Settings.Disabled>
    <!-- EN: RimTalk Button Display -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.ButtonDisplay>RimTalk边缘世谭按钮显示</RimTalk.Settings.ButtonDisplay>
    <!-- EN: Controls how the debug interface is accessed. 'Tab' adds a main tab, 'Toggle' shows an icon on the bottom bar, and 'None' hides it. -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.ButtonDisplayTooltip>控制如何访问调试界面。'Tab'添加主标签页，'Toggle'在底部栏显示图标，'None'隐藏它。</RimTalk.Settings.ButtonDisplayTooltip>
    
    <!-- EN: AI Instruction Prompt (Model: {0}) -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AIInstructionPrompt>AI指令提示（模型：{0}）</RimTalk.Settings.AIInstructionPrompt>
    <!-- EN: Tip: Use copy/paste with an external editor for multiline editing, or type \+n for new lines. -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.ExternalEditorTip>提示：使用外部编辑器的复制/粘贴功能进行多行编辑</RimTalk.Settings.ExternalEditorTip>
    <!-- EN: Tip: Pawn details (traits, relationships, race, age, etc.) are auto-included. Write generic instructions that work across all characters and colonies. -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.AutoIncludedTip>提示：角色详情（特质、关系、种族、年龄等）会自动包含。编写适用于所有角色和殖民地的通用指令。</RimTalk.Settings.AutoIncludedTip>
    <!-- EN: Warning: Longer prompts will consume more tokens and hit rate limits faster. No prompt caching is used. -->
  <RimTalk.Settings.RateLimitWarning>警告：更长的提示将消耗更多Tokens并更快达到速率限制。未使用提示缓存。</RimTalk.Settings.RateLimitWarning>
    <!-- EN: Tip: Adjust the bubble fade time in the Interaction Bubbles mod settings to keep dialogue visible longer during fast-forward play. -->
